     C                     ENDSR
** (MSGTBL)
E-01 INVALID OPTION.
E-02 INVALID SUPPLIER CODE.
E-03 INVALID PART NUMBER.
E-04 RECORD IS DELETED.
E-05 RECORD IS NOT FOUND.
E-06 EXCEEDED MAX RECORD NUMBER.
